1. Background 


On December 29, 1992, the EPA promulgated final regulations implementing the Early Reductions Program under section
112(i)(5) of the Clean Air Act, as amended (CAA), 42 U.S.C. 7412 (i)(5), 57 FR 61970 (December 29, 1992). As part of that
