1. The institution is designated as an eligible institution under the Strengthening Institutions Program (34 CFR
part 607) or the Strengthening Historically Black Colleges and Universities Program (34 CFR part 608). 

2. The institution requests that increased Federal share as part of its regular FSEOG funding application for that
year. 



